platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: The beloved Australian pupsBluey, Bingo, Chilli, and Banditare all here in Bluey: Lets Play! Featuring familiar characters and settings from the show, Bluey: Lets Play! will have your little ones frolicking with garden gnomes, hunting for hidden long dogs, and more.
The beloved Australian pups are all here! Featuring familiar characters and settings from the show, your little ones will be frolicking with garden gnomes and hunting for hidden long dogs.

Ladorable famille canine australienne est prsente au grand complet ! En retrouvant les personnages et les lieux de la srie qui leur sont familiers, vos enfants vont pouvoir samuser avec des gnomes de jardin ou des teckels cachs.
